
## Project Title: Skater Showdown

## Getting Started: 

Skater Showdown is an interactive web-based game where players can control a skater and perform tricks, competing against an opponent. The goal is to execute tricks successfully while avoiding wipeouts and accumulating the least number of letters in the word "SKATER."

## Link to Live Site:  https://bristeele99.github.io/

## Gameplay

- Choose a character (Tony Hawk or Estro Jen) at the beginning of the game.
- Click the "New Trick" button to reveal a random set of tricks.
- Press the corresponding keys to execute the tricks before your opponent does.
- Avoid wipeouts to prevent accumulating letters in the word "SKATER."
- The game continues until one player spells out the entire word "SKATER" and loses.

## Controls

- **Player 1 (Tony Hawk):** Use the provided buttons to control the game.
- **Player 2 (Opponent):** Use the provided buttons to control the game.

## Build Status:
