- After pressing the keys to complete a trick, the code will sometimes skip over certain if statements. 
- The Trick-List does not populate upon choosing a character.
- Extra characters with varying property values has not be configured or added to the game. 
- Additional Animation or Character Pics
- Having the logs populate on the top and not the bottom.
- Make the trick unavailable if you just hold. 
- Adding title above trick-list.
